@startuml
title Stock Movement Ledger

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false

class StockMovement {
  +id
  +productTypeId
  +storageId
  +documentType
  +documentId
  +direction
  +quantity
  +timestamp
}

class InventoryBalance {
  +storageId
  +productTypeId
  +quantityOnHand
}

class PurchaseReceipt
class SalesPosting
class Transfer
class Correction

PurchaseReceipt --> StockMovement : creates +
SalesPosting --> StockMovement : creates -
Transfer --> StockMovement : creates +/- pair
Correction --> StockMovement : creates delta
StockMovement --> InventoryBalance : projects to

note right of StockMovement
Primary truth should be why stock changed.
InventoryBalance remains the fast current-state view.
end note
@enduml
